headline: Could a Rotation Into Staples Stocks Be Next? What the Charts Say About 3 Dividend Payers.
summary: As the bull market rotates leadership across sectors, it may be time for consumer goods stocks to get their turn.  The consumer staples sector, a classic defensive play, has largely sat out the 2025 rally.
